        helper staff! We need help from developers, fundraisers,
        funders, and contributors to bring the new internet to the
        masses.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="meme-item">
      <div>
        <img src={meme4.src} />
        <h2>Web3</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Right now, Lume has only one full-time developer and limited
        helper staff! We need help from developers, fundraisers,
        funders, and contributors to bring the new internet to the
        masses.
      </p>
    </div>
